name: Cakara
description:
Cakara is a work that aims to be a representation of human nature, how they interact, and what eye candy is for them.

Cakara emphasizes the carnal nature of humans, which often do not have a significant distance from other species that considered as inferior.

Cakara is a reflection of the existence of a wild entity that resides under the auspices of humanity, which can ascend at any time and uncover the veil of humanity that has always been used as a distinguishing stamp between humans and other species.
